            <title>Version 0.8.1</title>
            <description><![CDATA[<h2>What's New in v0.8.1</h2><ul><li>**Dashboard stats reset on history clear** — Sessions, Words, and Time Saved are now lifetime counters stored independently. Clearing history no longer resets dashboard statistics.</li><li>**Large V3 Turbo model never finishes loading** — Incorrect model ID (`-turbo` → `_turbo`) prevented WhisperKit from finding the model. Existing users with the wrong ID are auto-migrated on launch.</li></ul>]]></description>
